    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment: 12 of 13 factors at or above required level. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the direct correspondence of the single ASTM F1717 condition to the COU and the conservative nature of the E/uval acceptance criterion. Model inputs factor achieves required level 3 based on the 2025-Q3 material property dataset; re-validation against the 2026-01-10 model revision geometry is planned for 2026-Q2 and will be documented in a subsequent credibility update. Decision: Accepted with commitment to complete re-validation.",
